Initalisierung
    - DIP-Schalter auslesen
         -> Sensornamen generieren
    - Publish (topic: discovery/send | payload: Sensorname)
    - Subscribe (topic: discovery/return | payload: Sensorname/XXX)
    - blockierendes Lesen (discovery/return)
    - Speichern empfangene Topic
    - Subscribe (topic: Sensorname/XXX/intervall)
    - Publish (topic: Sensorname/XXX/value)
    - Sensorkommmunikation konfigurieren

while (true)
{
    - Auslesen Sensor
    - Lesen (Sensornamen/XXX/intervall)
    - Sleep intervall
    - Publish (topic: Sensorname/XXX/value: value)
}